Description: Looking for a program reliable, efficient and uncomplicated to convert files? Well then you can not fail to try FormatFactory, one of the applications more intuitive to perform the conversion of videos, music and pictures on your computer.

Proof of this are the tens of millions of downloads it has in Baixaki, being the most downloaded software in its category. His biggest highlight is undoubtedly the ease of use.

If you've never dealt with applications of this kind, do not worry. The program interface is simple and pretty, with its conversion functions distributed by categories. Within each one, just choose the file format desired end among dozens of options available.
